<h1>HOME</h1>
<br>
<p class="mt-21 text-center text-xl">One Twenty-Seven is an IT company that creates different types of applications such as web apps, mobile apps, and stand-alone systems. It caters globally with current clients from US, Ireland, India, Vietnam and the Philippines. As of this writing, there are 254 employees with 112 working onsite in Baguio and the rest working from home/online. The office is a two-story building with each floor space having about 80 cubicles, four meeting rooms, five offices. On the first floor, there is a canteen with a snack bar (employees are outsourced), recreation rooms such as karaoke room, billiards table, music room complete with instruments, and outside is a spacious parking space, basketball court and swimming pool. </p>